channel.title: Compiling error, cant compile or compile clients
channel.description:
Got Windows 7 recently and saved my server, compiler and client and shit like that on a usb stick. Now when i have downloaded JDK, i cant compile, i can only RUN the server (which is bad). I also used Lin's Environment Variable setter - which made me think that it would help, but NO..NO..NO... What do i need to do? Before i used it, i made PATH & edited my Classpath... Still doesn't work, And before that - it didn't work out either. :mad:
Did i forget my brain in the bed today? ^^ :|
